name: Fluencerenderer
body:
## Fluence Renderer Project Report
### Darrin Willis - dswillis
This project implemented the infrastructure of a 2D ray-tracer.

Initially, it had fairly lofty goals of reproducing (this project)[https://benedikt-bitterli.me/tantalum/], however 
that ended up indeed being too lofty.
